Package: VancouvR
Type: Package
Title: Access The City of Vancouver Open Data API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jens von Bergmann
Maintainer: Jens von Bergmann <jens@mountainmath.ca>
Description: Wrapper around the City of Vancouver Open Data API to simplify and standardize access to CoV open data. 
  Functionality to list the data catalogue and access data and geographic records.
